{"title":"蹦蹦树","authors":["陈忠干"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":6,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦蹦树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈忠干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓小平同志1978年，以副总理的身份访问新加坡，在考察裕廊工业区时，为狮城人民栽下一棵蹦蹦树。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——手记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领袖林园有棵蹦蹦树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生龙活虎好威武："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国伟人亲手栽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狮城丰碑树千古！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦蹦树，蹦蹦树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦得绿叶茂盛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦得枝干圆粗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦得鲜花飘香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦得果实成熟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦蹦树，蹦蹦树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦出的情缘浓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦出的效益富："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦给路人一把艳阳伞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦给学童一篇教科书。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦蹦树，蹦蹦树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦洒狮城一片春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦洒地球万枝绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说伟人已远去？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹦蹦树，把他挽留住……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1999年于新加坡"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}